OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWidespread
OL,6,Fhazy sunshine and light winds this
OL,7,Fevening, then mostly fine and dry
OL,8,Fovernight. Chance of a few localised
OL,9,Fmist patches towards dawn in eastern
OL,10,Fareas and some patchy rain in the
OL,11,Fwest, but many places staying dry.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FGenerally dry and warm with
OL,14,Fplenty of hazy sunshine, although
OL,15,Fbriefly cloudier at times with a risk
OL,16,Fof showers, perhaps turning thundery
OL,17,Fby the evening. Locally breezy in
OL,18,Fcoastal areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
